# Futurnal Frontend Design System

Reference: [FRONTEND_DESIGN.md](mdc:FRONTEND_DESIGN.md)

## Design Philosophy
**"Sophisticated, Minimalist, Dark-Mode First"**
- Dark mode is the default and primary experience
- Keywords: Precision, Depth, Clarity, Sovereignty
- No accent colors - pure monochrome aesthetic

## Color Palette

