|-------|-------|----------|
| Background | `#000000` | `bg-black` |
| Text Primary | `#FFFFFF` | `text-white` |
| Text Secondary | `rgba(255,255,255,0.7)` | `text-white/70` |
| Text Tertiary | `rgba(255,255,255,0.5)` | `text-white/50` |
| Text Muted | `rgba(255,255,255,0.3)` | `text-white/30` |
