## Typography

### Fonts
- **Brand Headlines**: `Cinzel` (Google Fonts) - elegant serif
- **Taglines**: `Times New Roman` / `Georgia` (system serif, italic)

### CSS Classes
```css
.font-brand {
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.font-tagline {
  font-family: 'Times New Roman', 'Georgia', serif;
  font-style: italic;
}
```

### Usage
| Element | Classes |
|---------|---------|
| Page Title | `text-3xl font-brand tracking-wide text-white` |
| Tagline | `font-tagline italic text-white/40` |
| Body | `text-white/80` |
| Labels | `text-sm text-white/60` |

