### Theme-Aware Implementation
```tsx
const { resolvedTheme } = useTheme();
const logoSrc = resolvedTheme === 'dark' ? '/logo_dark.png' : '/logo.png';
```

## Component Patterns

### Buttons
- **Primary**: `bg-white text-black hover:bg-white/90` (dark mode)
- **Secondary**: `bg-transparent border border-white/30 text-white/70 hover:border-white/60`
- **Ghost**: `bg-transparent text-white/60 hover:text-white`
- **All buttons**: Sharp corners (no rounded), `transition-all`

### Inputs
```tsx
<input className="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white placeholder-white/30 focus:outline-none focus:border-white/30 transition-colors" />
```

### Cards
- Background: `bg-white/5`
- Border: `border border-white/10`
- No rounded corners
- Minimal shadows

## UI Copy Guidelines

### Do NOT Use
- "Ghost" as user-facing terminology
- "Animal" evolution references
- Colored accent elements

### Do Use
- "Personal knowledge graph"
- "AI evolution platform"
- "Personalized intelligence"
- Monochrome visual language

## Technical Stack

- **Framework**: React + Vite + Tauri (desktop), Next.js (landing)
- **Styling**: TailwindCSS v4 with `@tailwindcss/vite`
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Fonts**: Google Fonts (Cinzel) + System fonts

### Vite Config (Critical)
```typescript
// tailwindcss() MUST be before react()
plugins: [tailwindcss(), react()]
```
